sentences: Paweł Sęk (born 7 April 1977, Przemyśl) is a Polish producer, composer and audio engineer.
In 2000, Sek graduated from Berklee College of Music in Boston.
His credits include, Carrier, Frontier House - PBS, Beowulf - Trailer, KFC National Campaign, GM National TV ad, Audi National TV ad.
